thonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5026,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/men-silk\/","url_meta":{"origin":4035,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Silk: What can men do with silk?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: Umar bought a silk cloak from the market and took it to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, take it and wear it on Eid and when the delegations visit you.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThis clothing is for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/umar-faris-rum\/","url_meta":{"origin":4035,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Umar asks for the riches of Persia and Rome","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, call upon Allah to send abundance upon your nation, for the Persians and Romans enjoy abundance and have been given the world, yet they do not worship Allah as they recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3721,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/18\/zakat-al-fitr-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":4035,"position"